  "id": "nn_mn7t080n_w272sleel",
  "title": "javascript question answer",
  "content": "\n\n<h2 data-end=\"368\" data-start=\"284\">🟢 Q1. Difference between Synchronous and Asynchronous + Blocking vs Non-blocking</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"398\" data-start=\"370\">🧠 Your Answer (Refined)</h3>\n<p data-end=\"575\" data-start=\"399\">Synchronous tasks wo hote hain jo ek sequence me execute hote hain, ek ke baad ek, aur ek hi thread pe run karte hain. Jab tak ek task complete nahi hota, next start nahi hota.</p>\n<p data-end=\"630\" data-start=\"577\">Real-life: \"Mat hillo jab tak main paani laata hoon.\"</p>\n<p data-end=\"706\" data-start=\"632\">Asynchronous tasks me multiple kaam ek saath ho sakte hain bina wait kiye.</p>\n<p data-end=\"766\" data-start=\"708\">Real-life: \"Tum apna kaam karo, main coffee le aata hoon.\"</p>\n<p data-end=\"884\" data-start=\"768\">Blocking me program ruk jata hai jab tak task complete na ho jaye.<br data-end=\"837\" data-start=\"834\">\nNon-blocking me baaki ka code chalta rehta hai.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"889\" data-start=\"886\">\n<h3 data-end=\"913\" data-start=\"891\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"964\" data-start=\"914\">✔ Tumhara concept correct hai, bas ek clarity add:</p>\n<p data-end=\"1046\" data-start=\"966\">👉 <strong data-end=\"1002\" data-start=\"969\">Synchronous ≠ always blocking</strong><br data-end=\"1005\" data-start=\"1002\">\n👉 <strong data-end=\"1046\" data-start=\"1008\">Asynchronous ≠ always non-blocking</strong></p>\n<p data-end=\"1068\" data-start=\"1048\"><strong data-end=\"1068\" data-start=\"1048\">Best way to say:</strong></p>\n<ul data-end=\"1163\" data-start=\"1069\">\n<li data-end=\"1112\" data-start=\"1069\">\nSync → execution order define karta hai\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1163\" data-start=\"1113\">\nBlocking → execution behavior define karta hai\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1168\" data-start=\"1165\">\n<h2 data-end=\"1239\" data-start=\"1170\">🟢 Q2. How JavaScript handles async despite being single-threaded?</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"1269\" data-start=\"1241\">🧠 Your Answer (Refined)</h3>\n<p data-end=\"1367\" data-start=\"1270\">JavaScript single-threaded hai, lekin async tasks browser ya Node.js ke help se handle karta hai.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1484\" data-start=\"1369\">Call Stack functions execute karta hai (LIFO).<br data-end=\"1418\" data-start=\"1415\">\nAsync tasks Web APIs me chale jaate hain (setTimeout, DOM, fetch).</p>\n<p data-end=\"1615\" data-start=\"1486\">Wahan se callback register hota hai → Task Queue me jata hai → Event Loop check karta hai → stack empty hone pe execute hota hai.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1620\" data-start=\"1617\">\n<h3 data-end=\"1644\" data-start=\"1622\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"1704\" data-start=\"1645\">❌ Correction:<br>\n👉 Task Queue = <strong data-end=\"1704\" data-start=\"1675\">FIFO (First In First Out)</strong></p>\n<p data-end=\"1735\" data-start=\"1706\">बाकी explanation 🔥 solid hai</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1740\" data-start=\"1737\">\n<h2 data-end=\"1771\" data-start=\"1742\">🟢 Q3. Output predict karo</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"1866\" data-start=\"1773\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>console.log(\"A\");<br><br>setTimeout(() =&gt; {<br>  console.log(\"B\");<br>}, 0);<br><br>console.log(\"C\");</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<h3 data-end=\"1886\" data-start=\"1868\">🧠 Your Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"1908\" data-start=\"1887\">Output:<br data-end=\"1897\" data-start=\"1894\">\nA<br data-end=\"1901\" data-start=\"1898\">\nC<br data-end=\"1905\" data-start=\"1902\">\nB</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1913\" data-start=\"1910\">\n<h3 data-end=\"1937\" data-start=\"1915\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"1977\" data-start=\"1938\">✔ 100% correct<br data-end=\"1955\" data-start=\"1952\">\nExplanation bhi strong</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1982\" data-start=\"1979\">\n<h2 data-end=\"2021\" data-start=\"1984\">🟢 Q4. Event Bubbling vs Capturing</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"2051\" data-start=\"2023\">🧠 Your Answer (Refined)</h3>\n<p data-end=\"2122\" data-start=\"2052\">Event bubbling me event child se parent tak jata hai<br data-end=\"2107\" data-start=\"2104\">\n(IMG → LI → UL)</p>\n<p data-end=\"2218\" data-start=\"2124\">Capturing ke liye <code data-end=\"2171\" data-start=\"2142\">addEventListener(..., true)</code> use hota hai<br data-end=\"2187\" data-start=\"2184\">\nbut exactly flow clear nahi tha</p>\n<hr data-end=\"2223\" data-start=\"2220\">\n<h3 data-end=\"2247\" data-start=\"2225\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"2289\" data-start=\"2248\">👉 <strong data-end=\"2274\" data-start=\"2251\">Bubbling (default):</strong><br>\nChild → Parent</p>\n<p data-end=\"2323\" data-start=\"2291\">👉 <strong data-end=\"2308\" data-start=\"2294\">Capturing:</strong><br>\nParent → Child</p>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"2370\" data-start=\"2325\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>addEventListener(\"click\", fn, true)</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<hr data-end=\"2375\" data-start=\"2372\">\n<h2 data-end=\"2430\" data-start=\"2377\">🟢 Q5. Is <code data-end=\"2409\" data-start=\"2390\">setTimeout(fn, 0)</code> immediate execution?</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"2460\" data-start=\"2432\">🧠 Your Answer (Refined)</h3>\n<p data-end=\"2556\" data-start=\"2461\">setTimeout(fn, 0) immediate execute nahi hota<br data-end=\"2509\" data-start=\"2506\">\npehle Web API → Task Queue → Event Loop → Stack</p>\n<hr data-end=\"2561\" data-start=\"2558\">\n<h3 data-end=\"2585\" data-start=\"2563\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"2599\" data-start=\"2586\">❌ Correction:</p>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"2652\" data-start=\"2601\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>setTimeout(fn(), 0) ❌<br>setTimeout(fn, 0) ✅</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<p data-end=\"2704\" data-start=\"2654\">👉 <code data-end=\"2663\" data-start=\"2657\">fn()</code> turant execute ho jata hai (wrong usage)</p>\n<hr data-end=\"2709\" data-start=\"2706\">\n<h2 data-end=\"2745\" data-start=\"2711\">🟢 Q6. Ways to add events in JS</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"2775\" data-start=\"2747\">🧠 Your Answer (Refined)</h3>\n<ol data-end=\"2791\" data-start=\"2777\">\n<li data-end=\"2791\" data-start=\"2777\">\nInline HTML\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"2834\" data-start=\"2792\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>&lt;img onclick=\"alert('hello')\"&gt;</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<p data-end=\"2849\" data-start=\"2835\">❌ Not scalable</p>\n<ol data-end=\"2864\" data-start=\"2851\" start=\"2\">\n<li data-end=\"2864\" data-start=\"2851\">\nJS onclick\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"2895\" data-start=\"2865\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>element.onclick = fn</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<p data-end=\"2906\" data-start=\"2896\">⚠️ Limited</p>\n<ol data-end=\"2929\" data-start=\"2908\" start=\"3\">\n<li data-end=\"2929\" data-start=\"2908\">\naddEventListener ✅\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"2977\" data-start=\"2930\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>element.addEventListener(\"click\", fn)</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<hr data-end=\"2982\" data-start=\"2979\">\n<h3 data-end=\"3006\" data-start=\"2984\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"3026\" data-start=\"3007\">✔ Perfect answer 🔥</p>\n<hr data-end=\"3031\" data-start=\"3028\">\n<h2 data-end=\"3064\" data-start=\"3033\">🟢 Q7. Event bubbling output</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"3230\" data-start=\"3066\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>parent.addEventListener(\"click\", () =&gt; {<br>  console.log(\"Parent clicked\");<br>});<br><br>child.addEventListener(\"click\", () =&gt; {<br>  console.log(\"Child clicked\");<br>});</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<h3 data-end=\"3250\" data-start=\"3232\">🧠 Your Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"3300\" data-start=\"3251\">Parent clicked<br data-end=\"3268\" data-start=\"3265\">\nChild clicked<br data-end=\"3284\" data-start=\"3281\">\nParent clicked</p>\n<hr data-end=\"3305\" data-start=\"3302\">\n<h3 data-end=\"3329\" data-start=\"3307\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"3341\" data-start=\"3330\">❌ Incorrect</p>\n<p data-end=\"3360\" data-start=\"3343\">✔ Correct Output:</p>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"3397\" data-start=\"3361\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>Child clicked<br>Parent clicked</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<p data-end=\"3437\" data-start=\"3399\">👉 Bubbling → child first, then parent</p>\n<hr data-end=\"3442\" data-start=\"3439\">\n<h2 data-end=\"3476\" data-start=\"3444\">🟢 Q8. Stop event propagation</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"3506\" data-start=\"3478\">🧠 Your Answer (Refined)</h3>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"3591\" data-start=\"3508\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>element.addEventListener(\"click\", function(e){<br>  e.stopPropagation();<br>});</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<hr data-end=\"3596\" data-start=\"3593\">\n<h3 data-end=\"3620\" data-start=\"3598\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"3664\" data-start=\"3621\">✔ Correct<br data-end=\"3633\" data-start=\"3630\">\n❌ spelling: <code data-end=\"3664\" data-start=\"3645\">stopPropagation()</code></p>\n<hr data-end=\"3669\" data-start=\"3666\">\n<h2 data-end=\"3716\" data-start=\"3671\">🟢 Q9. event.target vs event.currentTarget</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"3736\" data-start=\"3718\">🧠 Your Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"3778\" data-start=\"3737\">target pata hai<br data-end=\"3755\" data-start=\"3752\">\ncurrentTarget nahi pata</p>\n<hr data-end=\"3783\" data-start=\"3780\">\n<h3 data-end=\"3807\" data-start=\"3785\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<div><div tabindex=\"-1\"><table data-end=\"3931\" data-start=\"3809\"><thead data-end=\"3831\" data-start=\"3809\"><tr data-end=\"3831\" data-start=\"3809\"><th data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"3820\" data-start=\"3809\">Property</th><th data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"3831\" data-start=\"3820\">Meaning</th></tr></thead><tbody data-end=\"3931\" data-start=\"3852\"><tr data-end=\"3887\" data-start=\"3852\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"3861\" data-start=\"3852\">target</td><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"3887\" data-start=\"3861\">actual clicked element</td></tr><tr data-end=\"3931\" data-start=\"3888\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"3904\" data-start=\"3888\">currentTarget</td><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"3931\" data-start=\"3904\">jahan listener laga hai</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>\n<hr data-end=\"3936\" data-start=\"3933\">\n<h2 data-end=\"3960\" data-start=\"3938\">🟢 Q10. Bug in code</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"4111\" data-start=\"3962\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>document.querySelector(\"#images\").addEventListener(\"click\", function(e){<br>    let removeIt = e.target.parentNode;<br>    removeIt.remove();<br>});</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<h3 data-end=\"4141\" data-start=\"4113\">🧠 Your Answer (Refined)</h3>\n<p data-end=\"4215\" data-start=\"4142\">Bug: agar LI ya UL pe click ho gaya toh galat element remove ho sakta hai</p>\n<p data-end=\"4221\" data-start=\"4217\">Fix:</p>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"4325\" data-start=\"4223\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>if(e.target.tagName === \"IMG\"){<br>  let removeIt = e.target.parentNode;<br>  removeIt.remove();<br>}</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<hr data-end=\"4330\" data-start=\"4327\">\n<h3 data-end=\"4354\" data-start=\"4332\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"4400\" data-start=\"4355\">✔ PERFECT 🔥 (real-world level understanding)</p>\n<hr data-end=\"4405\" data-start=\"4402\">\n<h1 data-end=\"4424\" data-start=\"4407\">🧠 SET 1 RESULT</h1>\n<div><div tabindex=\"-1\"><table data-end=\"4567\" data-start=\"4426\"><thead data-end=\"4443\" data-start=\"4426\"><tr data-end=\"4443\" data-start=\"4426\"><th data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4433\" data-start=\"4426\">Area</th><th data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4443\" data-start=\"4433\">Status</th></tr></thead><tbody data-end=\"4567\" data-start=\"4462\"><tr data-end=\"4490\" data-start=\"4462\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4478\" data-start=\"4462\">Concept clarity</td><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4490\" data-start=\"4478\">✅ Strong</td></tr><tr data-end=\"4514\" data-start=\"4491\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4504\" data-start=\"4491\">Event system</td><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4514\" data-start=\"4504\">✅ Good</td></tr><tr data-end=\"4538\" data-start=\"4515\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4528\" data-start=\"4515\">Async basics</td><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4538\" data-start=\"4528\">✅ Good</td></tr><tr data-end=\"4567\" data-start=\"4539\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4557\" data-start=\"4539\">Critical mistakes</td><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4567\" data-start=\"4557\">⚠️ Few</td></tr></tbody></table><br></div></div><div tabindex=\"-1\">\n\n<h1 data-end=\"104\" data-start=\"84\">🟢 SET 2 (Q11–Q20)</h1>\n<hr data-end=\"109\" data-start=\"106\">\n<h2 data-end=\"162\" data-start=\"111\">🟢 Q11. Remove image on click (event delegation)</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"192\" data-start=\"164\">🧠 Your Answer (Refined)</h3>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"381\" data-start=\"194\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>document.querySelector(\"#images\").addEventListener(\"click\", function(e){<br>  if(e.target.tagName === \"IMG\"){<br>    let removeIt = e.target.parentNode;<br>    removeIt.remove();<br>  }<br>});</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<hr data-end=\"386\" data-start=\"383\">\n<h3 data-end=\"410\" data-start=\"388\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"481\" data-start=\"411\">✔ 100% correct 🔥<br data-end=\"431\" data-start=\"428\">\n👉 Ye <strong data-end=\"477\" data-start=\"437\">event delegation ka perfect use-case</strong> hai</p>\n<hr data-end=\"486\" data-start=\"483\">\n<h2 data-end=\"532\" data-start=\"488\">🟢 Q12. preventDefault vs stopPropagation</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"562\" data-start=\"534\">🧠 Your Answer (Refined)</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"676\" data-start=\"564\">\n<li data-end=\"623\" data-start=\"564\">\n<strong data-end=\"586\" data-start=\"566\">preventDefault()</strong> → default browser action rokta hai\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"676\" data-start=\"624\">\n<strong data-end=\"647\" data-start=\"626\">stopPropagation()</strong> → event bubbling rokta hai\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-end=\"757\" data-start=\"678\">Use together jab:<br>\n👉 custom behavior chahiye + parent trigger nahi hona chahiye</p>\n<hr data-end=\"762\" data-start=\"759\">\n<h3 data-end=\"808\" data-start=\"764\">💯 Improved Answer (with strong example)</h3>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"972\" data-start=\"810\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>link.addEventListener(\"click\", (e) =&gt; {<br>  e.preventDefault();     // link open nahi hoga<br>  e.stopPropagation();    // parent event trigger nahi hoga<br>});</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<p data-end=\"1013\" data-start=\"974\">✔ Concept correct, bas example weak tha</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1018\" data-start=\"1015\">\n<h2 data-end=\"1052\" data-start=\"1020\">🟢 Q13. Prevent link redirect</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"1082\" data-start=\"1054\">🧠 Your Answer (Refined)</h3>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"1218\" data-start=\"1084\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>document.querySelector(\"#google\").addEventListener(\"click\", function(e){<br>  e.preventdefault();<br>  console.log(\"Clicked\");<br>});</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<hr data-end=\"1223\" data-start=\"1220\">\n<h3 data-end=\"1247\" data-start=\"1225\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"1258\" data-start=\"1248\">❌ Mistake:</p>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"1311\" data-start=\"1260\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>e.preventdefault() ❌<br>e.preventDefault() ✅</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<p data-end=\"1342\" data-start=\"1313\">👉 JS case-sensitive hota hai</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1347\" data-start=\"1344\">\n<h2 data-end=\"1374\" data-start=\"1349\">🟢 Q14. Output predict</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"1496\" data-start=\"1376\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>console.log(1);<br><br>setTimeout(() =&gt; console.log(2), 1000);<br>setTimeout(() =&gt; console.log(3), 0);<br><br>console.log(4);</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<h3 data-end=\"1516\" data-start=\"1498\">🧠 Your Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"1532\" data-start=\"1517\">1<br data-end=\"1521\" data-start=\"1518\">\n4<br data-end=\"1525\" data-start=\"1522\">\n3<br data-end=\"1529\" data-start=\"1526\">\n2</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1537\" data-start=\"1534\">\n<h3 data-end=\"1561\" data-start=\"1539\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"1576\" data-start=\"1562\">✔ Correct 🔥</p>\n<p data-end=\"1588\" data-start=\"1578\">👉 Reason:</p>\n<ul data-end=\"1647\" data-start=\"1589\">\n<li data-end=\"1623\" data-start=\"1589\">\n3 → pehle queue me aayega (0 ms)\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1647\" data-start=\"1624\">\n2 → baad me (1000 ms)\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1652\" data-start=\"1649\">\n<h2 data-end=\"1685\" data-start=\"1654\">🟢 Q15. setInterval behavior</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"1715\" data-start=\"1687\">🧠 Your Answer (Refined)</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1814\" data-start=\"1716\">\n<li data-end=\"1743\" data-start=\"1716\">\nYe kabhi stop nahi hota\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1779\" data-start=\"1744\">\nclearInterval() se hi rukta hai\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1814\" data-start=\"1780\">\ncontinuous execution karta hai\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1819\" data-start=\"1816\">\n<h3 data-end=\"1843\" data-start=\"1821\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"1855\" data-start=\"1844\">✔ Correct</p>\n<p data-end=\"1917\" data-start=\"1857\">👉 Add this:<br>\n⚠️ Memory leak / performance issue ho sakta hai</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1922\" data-start=\"1919\">\n<h2 data-end=\"1951\" data-start=\"1924\">🟢 Q16. Fix interval bug</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"1971\" data-start=\"1953\">🧠 Your Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"1992\" data-start=\"1972\">“koi issue nahi hai”</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1997\" data-start=\"1994\">\n<h3 data-end=\"2021\" data-start=\"1999\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"2068\" data-start=\"2022\">❌ Major mistake (important interview question)</p>\n<p data-end=\"2081\" data-start=\"2070\">👉 Problem:</p>\n<ul data-end=\"2132\" data-start=\"2082\">\n<li data-end=\"2132\" data-start=\"2082\">\nHar click pe <strong data-end=\"2132\" data-start=\"2097\">new interval create ho raha hai</strong>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2137\" data-start=\"2134\">\n<h3 data-end=\"2157\" data-start=\"2139\">✅ Correct Fix:</h3>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"2362\" data-start=\"2159\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>let intervalId;<br><br>document.querySelector(\"#start\").addEventListener(\"click\", () =&gt; {<br>  if (!intervalId) {<br>    intervalId = setInterval(() =&gt; {<br>      console.log(\"Running\");<br>    }, 1000);<br>  }<br>});</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<hr data-end=\"2367\" data-start=\"2364\">\n<h2 data-end=\"2405\" data-start=\"2369\">🟢 Q17. setTimeout vs setInterval</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"2435\" data-start=\"2407\">🧠 Your Answer (Refined)</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2508\" data-start=\"2437\">\n<li data-end=\"2474\" data-start=\"2437\">\nsetTimeout → ek baar run hota hai\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2508\" data-start=\"2475\">\nsetInterval → repeat hota hai\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-end=\"2520\" data-start=\"2510\">Real-life:</p>\n<ul data-end=\"2581\" data-start=\"2521\">\n<li data-end=\"2548\" data-start=\"2521\">\ntimeout → delayed alert\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2581\" data-start=\"2549\">\ninterval → repeated reminder\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2586\" data-start=\"2583\">\n<h3 data-end=\"2610\" data-start=\"2588\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"2644\" data-start=\"2611\">✔ Perfect 🔥<br data-end=\"2626\" data-start=\"2623\">\n👉 Interview-ready</p>\n<hr data-end=\"2649\" data-start=\"2646\">\n<h2 data-end=\"2684\" data-start=\"2651\">🟢 Q18. Execution flow explain</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"2797\" data-start=\"2686\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>console.log(\"Start\");<br><br>setTimeout(() =&gt; {<br>  console.log(\"Async Task\");<br>}, 2000);<br><br>console.log(\"End\");</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<h3 data-end=\"2817\" data-start=\"2799\">🧠 Your Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"2829\" data-start=\"2818\">(skip kiya)</p>\n<hr data-end=\"2834\" data-start=\"2831\">\n<h3 data-end=\"2858\" data-start=\"2836\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"2876\" data-start=\"2860\">👉 Step-by-step:</p>\n<ol data-end=\"3050\" data-start=\"2878\">\n<li data-end=\"2911\" data-start=\"2878\">\n\"Start\" → Call Stack → print\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2951\" data-start=\"2912\">\nsetTimeout → Web API me chala gaya\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2970\" data-start=\"2952\">\n\"End\" → print\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3010\" data-start=\"2971\">\n2 sec baad → callback → Task Queue\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3050\" data-start=\"3011\">\nEvent Loop → stack empty → execute\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr data-end=\"3055\" data-start=\"3052\">\n<h3 data-end=\"3076\" data-start=\"3057\">✅ Final Output:</h3>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"3117\" data-start=\"3077\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>Start<br>End<br>Async Task</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<hr data-end=\"3122\" data-start=\"3119\">\n<h2 data-end=\"3157\" data-start=\"3124\">🟢 Q19. When async is NOT good</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"3187\" data-start=\"3159\">🧠 Your Answer (Refined)</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"3266\" data-start=\"3189\">\n<li data-end=\"3198\" data-start=\"3189\">\nLogin\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3224\" data-start=\"3199\">\nPassword verification\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3245\" data-start=\"3225\">\nBank transaction\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3266\" data-start=\"3246\">\nOTP verification\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-end=\"3318\" data-start=\"3268\">👉 Inme pehle validation complete hona zaroori hai</p>\n<hr data-end=\"3323\" data-start=\"3320\">\n<h3 data-end=\"3347\" data-start=\"3325\">💯 Improved Answer</h3>\n<p data-end=\"3384\" data-start=\"3348\">✔ Excellent 🔥 (real-world thinking)</p>\n<hr data-end=\"3389\" data-start=\"3386\">\n<h2 data-end=\"3434\" data-start=\"3391\">🟢 Q20. Background color changer project</h2>\n<h3 data-end=\"3472\" data-start=\"3436\">🧠 Your Answer (Refined Summary)</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"3551\" data-start=\"3474\">\n<li data-end=\"3500\" data-start=\"3474\">\nStart → interval start\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3525\" data-start=\"3501\">\nStop → clearInterval\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3551\" data-start=\"3526\">\nRandom color generate\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"3556\" data-start=\"3553\">\n<h3 data-end=\"3571\" data-start=\"3558\">❌ Issues:</h3>\n<ol data-end=\"3693\" data-start=\"3573\">\n<li data-end=\"3616\" data-start=\"3573\">\n❌ Multiple interval protection missing\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3651\" data-start=\"3617\">\n❌ <code data-end=\"3641\" data-start=\"3622\">intervalId = null</code> missing\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"3693\" data-start=\"3652\">\n❌ Color logic wrong (only 0–9, no A–F)\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr data-end=\"3698\" data-start=\"3695\">\n<h3 data-end=\"3723\" data-start=\"3700\">💯 Improved Version</h3>\n<div class=\"code-block-wrapper\" contenteditable=\"false\"><button class=\"copy-code-btn\">Copy</button><pre data-end=\"4258\" data-start=\"3725\" contenteditable=\"true\"><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"code-block-viewer\"><div><div>let intervalId;<br><br>function randomColor(){<br>  const hex = \"0123456789ABCDEF\";<br>  let color = \"#\";<br><br>  for(let i = 0; i &lt; 6; i++){<br>    color += hex[Math.floor(Math.random() * 16)];<br>  }<br><br>  return color;<br>}<br><br>document.querySelector(\"#start\").addEventListener(\"click\", () =&gt; {<br>  if(!intervalId){<br>    intervalId = setInterval(() =&gt; {<br>      document.body.style.backgroundColor = randomColor();<br>    }, 1000);<br>  }<br>});<br><br>document.querySelector(\"#stop\").addEventListener(\"click\", () =&gt; {<br>  clearInterval(intervalId);<br>  intervalId = null;<br>});</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div></div></div></pre></div>\n<hr data-end=\"4263\" data-start=\"4260\">\n<h1 data-end=\"4294\" data-start=\"4265\">🧠 FINAL EVALUATION (SET 2)</h1>\n<div><div tabindex=\"-1\"><table data-end=\"4516\" data-start=\"4296\"><thead data-end=\"4313\" data-start=\"4296\"><tr data-end=\"4313\" data-start=\"4296\"><th data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4303\" data-start=\"4296\">Area</th><th data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4313\" data-start=\"4303\">Status</th></tr></thead><tbody data-end=\"4516\" data-start=\"4332\"><tr data-end=\"4362\" data-start=\"4332\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4349\" data-start=\"4332\">Event Delegation</td><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4362\" data-start=\"4349\">🔥 Strong</td></tr><tr data-end=\"4393\" data-start=\"4363\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4383\" data-start=\"4363\">Async Understanding</td><td data-end=\"4393\" data-start=\"4383\" data-col-size=\"sm\">✅ Good</td></tr><tr data-end=\"4427\" data-start=\"4394\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4414\" data-start=\"4394\">Real-world thinking</td><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4427\" data-start=\"4414\">🔥 Strong</td></tr><tr data-end=\"4456\" data-start=\"4428\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4442\" data-start=\"4428\">Bugs spotting</td><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4456\" data-start=\"4442\">⚠️ Improve</td></tr><tr data-end=\"4516\" data-start=\"4457\"><td data-col-size=\"sm\" data-end=\"4477\" data-start=\"4457\">Attention to detail</td><td data-end=\"4516\" data-start=\"4477\" data-col-size=\"sm\">⚠️ (case sensitivity, interval bug)</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>\n<hr data-end=\"4521\" data-start=\"4518\">\n<h1 data-end=\"4547\" data-start=\"4523\">🏁 FINAL OVERALL LEVEL</h1>\n<p data-end=\"4597\" data-start=\"4549\">👉 <strong data-end=\"4597\" data-start=\"4552\">You are now: ~70–75% JS Foundations Clear</strong></p>\n<hr data-end=\"4602\" data-start=\"4599\">\n<h1 data-end=\"4630\" data-start=\"4604\">🚨 What you MUST fix now</h1>\n<ul data-end=\"4761\" data-start=\"4632\">\n<li data-end=\"4669\" data-start=\"4632\">\nCase sensitivity (<code data-end=\"4668\" data-start=\"4652\">preventDefault</code>)\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"4692\" data-start=\"4670\">\nQueue concept (FIFO)\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"4712\" data-start=\"4693\">\nCapturing clarity\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"4745\" data-start=\"4713\">\nInterval bugs (VERY IMPORTANT)\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"4761\" data-start=\"4746\">\ncurrentTarget\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<br></div><div tabindex=\"-1\"><br></div>\n\n",
